    "In order to elucidate finite-size effects, we study the relaxation dynamics for different system sizes and for different values of J/t 0.",
    "We observe that system-size dependencies in the time evolution depend significantly on the value of J/t 0.",
    "For L = 216, the finite-size effects typically appear around t • t 0 ∼ 100 for small J/t 0 and around t • t 0 ∼ 80 for large J/t 0 (results not shown here).",
